issue.title: *** FAQ: How To Migrate Gazebo9 Controller(s) to Ignition ***

content.raw: I don’t think “All of them” is the correct answer to Q8. For example, you have tiles for the urban circuit in the repo. But also, there are tunnel circuit tiles that are not used in the practice worlds, and look substantially different \(or did a few days ago, at least\). There are also artifacts \(radio, caving helmet\), which are not specified as tunnel circuit artifacts in the competition guide.
content.html: I don’t think “All of them” is the correct answer to Q8. For example, you have tiles for the urban circuit in the repo. But also, there are tunnel circuit tiles that are not used in the practice worlds, and look substantially different (or did a few days ago, at least). There are also artifacts (radio, caving helmet), which are not specified as tunnel circuit artifacts in the competition guide.
